high_descs: Turn to the left and locate the sink.
Open the bottom cabinet directly under the sink and take out the ladle. Shut the door.
Place the ladle in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the ladle.
Move a step to the right to continue facing the counter.
Open the right bottom cabinet and place the ladle inside. Shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a ladle and put it in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink.
Open the cabinet and grab the ladle.
Place the ladle in the sink.
Rinse off the ladle in the sink.
Turn to the left and face the cabinets.
Open the rightmost cabinet and place the ladle inside.
anns.task_desc: Place the washed ladle in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight to the sink.
Take the measuring spoon out of the cabinet under the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Turn left and face the left side of the counter.
Place the measuring spoon in the bottom right cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed measuring spoon in a cabinet.
